column2: SELECT o.GALname, o.ra, o.dec, o.z, p.objId, p.petroFlux_u, p.petroFlux_g, p.petroFlux_r, p.petroFlux_i, p.petroFlux_z, p.petroFluxErr_u, p.petroFluxErr_g, p.petroFluxErr_r, p.petroFluxErr_i, p.petroFluxErr_z INTO mydb.pisco_sdss_petroflux FROM mydb.pisco_final_galaxies as o CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (o.ra, o.dec, #) AS near INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary AS pp ON pp.objID = near.objID INNER JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID = pp.objID INNER JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON pp.objID = p.objID
